---
description: GUI layer conventions (DearPyGui) and headless requirement
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

- pxlreact's GUI layer uses DearPyGui: `pxl_statusbar.py` (in-process runtime status bar) and
`pxl_editor.py` (separate-process profile.json editor); do not introduce tkinter or other GUI
frameworks, and ignore any legacy notes referring to tkinter, pxl_gui.py, or pxl_guiconst.py
- The core must remain fully functional headless: gui.statusbar_enabled = false in settings.toml
disables the status bar, and no core module may import dearpygui at module level
